Hi everyone.

Sorry if I am OT, but reading the caml-list I'm having difficulties 
reading some threads.
The problem seems to be this: when someone posts a message to the 
caml-list, message arrives to every subscriber with the email of the 
sender in the from field. That's ok.
But when someone replies, can happen that he/she replies just to the 
sender (that means privately).
To reply to the list he/she must manually change the to field in his/her 
mail client.

Now, is it possible to set the Reply To field into the e-main forwarded 
by Caml-list to have an automatic follow-up to the list?

Thanks
LP

